        {
            "title": "財經｜大新銀行(02356)去年盈利升兩成 息0.49元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜大新銀行(02356)去年盈利升兩成 息0.49元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜大新銀行(02356)去年盈利升兩成 息0.49元</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大新銀行(02356)公布截至2025年12月底止年度業績，股東應佔盈利24.76億元，按年增長20.16%，每股盈利1.76元，派末期息0.49元，全年股息共0.8元，按年增加21.21%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，淨利息收入58.29億元，按年增長10.22%，而非利息收入則增加27%至20.87億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">展望2026年，該行的重心仍將集中於可控範疇，包括嚴謹的成本管理、對增長領域進行選擇性投資，以及維持強健的資產負債表，相信此審慎策略將使該行能夠有效應對未來的市場發展，同時使集團處於有利位置，以在未來穩步前進。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期的中東事件反映全球風險仍然存在，該行預計此類風險在短期內將維持高企。集團將維持審慎保守，保持強韌的財務狀況，同時尋求符合策略之機遇，以為股東創造可持續的回報。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C-02356-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E5%8D%87%E5%85%A9%E6%88%90-%E6%81%AF0-044816610.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 12:50:22",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛因能源價格影響下調日本東證指數目標",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/96rpNewOLVt7Kw59K1.Ucw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB6200T_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 高盛週日下調了對日本東證指數的目標,理由是由於中東戰爭持續導致能源價格上漲,預期盈利增長將放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛將東證指數3個月、6個月和12個月目標分別下調至3,800點、4,000點和4,200點,此前目標分別為3,900點、4,100點和4,300點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該投資銀行表示,此次下調是由於預期荷姆茲海峽持續中斷將導致石油和天然氣價格上漲。這是因為美國與以色列對伊朗的戰爭幾乎沒有降溫跡象,週末葉門胡塞武裝襲擊以色列後,戰事可能進入新的前線。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dec71363-86f1-3099-8db2-298826ff349e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛將東證指數2026財年每股盈利增長預估從衝突開始前的12.3%下調至7.2%,假設荷姆茲海峽中斷影響持續六週為基本情境。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該銀行表示,市場情緒仍然脆弱,並補充說,對中東衝突迅速解決的預期已大幅降低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東證指數在3月份錄得10.2%的跌幅,受到伊朗戰爭爆發的打擊。東證指數的下跌是因為市場預期日本經濟將面臨更多與能源相關的中斷,以及荷姆茲海峽航運活動減少導致的更廣泛供應鏈中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月份的跌幅將終結東證指數連續11個月的漲勢——在過去一年中,該指數曾創下一系列歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛指出,以國內市場為主的日本股票仍然表現強勁,保險公司和防禦性股票也是如此。製藥和醫療保健類股在近幾週表現尤為突出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E5%9B%A0%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9D%B1%E8%AD%89%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-055350202.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 14:20:22",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國｜國家市監總局：著力防治平台經濟、光伏、鋰電池、新能源汽車等重點行業和領域「內捲式」競爭",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中國｜國家市監總局：著力防治平台經濟、光伏、鋰電池、新能源汽車等重點行業和領域「內捲式」競爭\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國｜國家市監總局：著力防治平台經濟、光伏、鋰電池、新能源汽車等重點行業和領域「內捲式」競爭</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國家市場監管總局發表關於進一步貫徹實施《中華人民共和國反不正當競爭法》的通知。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中提到，綜合運用各類反不正當競爭措施，著力防治平台經濟、光伏、鋰電池、新能源汽車等重點行業和領域「內捲式」競爭。精準辨識和依法查處平台企業無正當理由，利用搜索排名、經營評價、算法控制、限制流量、下架商品、增加費用、拖欠賬期、中止交易、內部懲戒等手段，或在補貼、優惠、紅包、折扣、「滿減」、「買贈」、促銷等活動中，強制或者變相強制平台內經營者以低於成本的價格銷售商品，擾亂市場競爭秩序。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6669bbc8-f4fe-352a-85e3-d5350209e28b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對個案進行違法判定時，要綜合考慮交易標的性質、生產規模和類型、市場和銷售情況、生產效率和技術、商品或服務品質等多方面因素。壓實平台經營者處置不正當競爭行為的責任義務，督促平台明確平台內公平競爭規則，建立專門工作機制，接受舉報投訴，做好糾紛處置，及時採取必要措施處置不正當競爭行為，保存有關記錄並報告執法機構。防止平台經營者借審核管理不當干預平台內經營者的自主經營權。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
